Introduction

Jungmin is a South Korean trainee under SM Entertainment. He is a former pre-debut member of the boy group NCT and its sub-unit NCT Wish.

On July 12, 2023, Jungmin, was revealed as a contestant of SM Entertainment's NCT Universe : LASTART. He ranked 4th, thus making him a member of NCT Wish.

On October 2, 2023, SM Entertainment announced that Jungmin would depart from the group and return to be a trainee due to health concerns. NCT Wish would continue their activities with six members.
